metadata.name: DWA - The Project
metadata.description:
Paus Limited

 The collectors of this NFT will receive & include:
- Supporter NFT - This NFT represents support for the film and can be kept as a collectible souvenir or resold.
- Early Access to the film - This NFT gives buyers a chance to watch the film first then enyoneelse on Paus Vault This privilege is granted to NFT holders only, but buyers can transfer to another user or resell on the secondary market.
